Virginia – For denied appeals, visit the Virginia Attorney General’s Office, Consumer Protection Division.
ShareThis is a member of the following self-regulatory programs:
Network Advertising Initiative (NAI):
ShareThis is a member in good standing with the NAI. The NAI offers an online
web opt-out platform
to allow consumers to express their choices and provides general information related to privacy and
Interest Based Advertising
.
The Digital Advertising Alliance (DAA):
ShareThis adheres to the Digital Advertising Alliance Self-Regulatory Principles for Online Behavioral Advertising.  The
DAA opt-out platform
offers the consumer a choice page to opt out from advertising services, and general information related to privacy.
